OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to all offences and
OL,7,Fwas sentenced to 38 months'
OL,8,Fimprisonment at Lewes Crown Court on
OL,9,F14 October.
OL,11,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,12,FConstable Jim Austin, said: "The
OL,13,Fproperties associated with Veness were
OL,14,Fclearly adapted to produce and supply
OL,15,Fillegal drugs in order to fund his
OL,16,Flavish lifestyle. His high value
OL,17,Fpossessions ` including super car,
OL,18,Fluxury watch and designer clothing `
OL,19,Fsuggest he generated significant
OL,20,Fincome from his criminality.
